sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent as Agent
    participant Ext as Extension
    participant Provide as provide API
    participant Consume as consume API

    Note over Agent,Ext: During enable():
    Ext->>Ext: context.provide.tool('my_tool', fn)
    Provide->>Agent: add to agent.tools array
    Ext->>Ext: context.on('turn_end', handler)
    Agent->>Ext: event handler invoked later

    Note over Agent,Ext: During agent run:
    Agent->>Agent: emit('message_end', msg)
    Agent->>Ext: on('message_end') called
    Ext->>Ext: handler logic

    Note over Agent,Ext: Resource consumption:
    Ext->>Consume: context.consume('prompt:base')
    Consume->>Provide: lookup provided resource
    Provide-->>Ext: return definition
    Ext->>Ext: use consumed resource

    Note over Agent,Ext: Suppose another extension provides a transformContext hook:
    Agent->>Agent: Before LLM call
    Agent->>Provide: call all transformContext hooks in order
    Provide->>Ext1: hook1(messages)
    Ext1-->>Provide: modified
    Provide->>Ext2: hook2(modified)
    Ext2-->>Provide: further modified
    Provide-->>Agent: final messages
    Agent->>Agent: convertToLlm and send